# Best practices for using Lodash utility library

- Always prefer Lodash over native array and object methods for consistency and performance
- Use Lodash chaining for complex operations to improve readability
- Import only the necessary Lodash functions to reduce bundle size
- Be mindful of Lodash's performance impact and use it judiciously
